1
00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:10,300
♪The stars in the sky shine bright♪

2
00:00:10,300 --> 00:00:14,660
♪The rippling water reflects your face♪

3
00:00:14,940 --> 00:00:18,340
♪No one knows the struggle in my mind♪

4
00:00:18,340 --> 00:00:22,020
♪I act calm as I say hi♪

5
00:00:22,020 --> 00:00:24,140
♪In two different worlds♪

6
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,060
♪we're both rushing ahead♪

7
00:00:26,060 --> 00:00:29,820
♪Thinking the view at the top
would leave us breathless♪

8
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:33,860
♪As memories fade like shattered pieces♪

9
00:00:33,860 --> 00:00:37,620
♪I still find myself drawn to you♪

10
00:00:37,620 --> 00:00:41,420
♪In a crowd of people,
with nowhere to land♪

11
00:00:41,420 --> 00:00:45,460
♪Your presence is my island,
my solid ground♪

12
00:00:45,460 --> 00:00:50,220
♪I know where you are,
but act like I don't care♪

13
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:53,580
♪My heart beats for you,
yet I leave it unsaid♪

14
00:00:55,420 --> 00:00:58,700
[This World Is Not Real]
[Load game]

15
00:00:58,740 --> 00:01:01,700
[Episode 15]

16
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,390
Qing Wan, let me explain.

17
00:01:11,170 --> 00:01:12,000
Qing Wan!

18
00:01:26,780 --> 00:01:27,370
Lin Xian!

19
00:01:30,310 --> 00:01:30,920
Lin Xian.

20
00:01:32,610 --> 00:01:33,160
Lin Xian,

21
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:33,810
wake up!

22
00:01:34,090 --> 00:01:35,090
Wan, are you okay?

23
00:01:35,730 --> 00:01:36,470
Lin Xian!

24
00:01:38,420 --> 00:01:39,000
Wake up!

25
00:01:39,740 --> 00:01:40,520
Hey!

26
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,370
Can you drive?

27
00:01:42,780 --> 00:01:44,300
- I'm talking to you!
- I need an ambulance!

28
00:01:45,780 --> 00:01:46,590
What are you doing?

29
00:01:46,970 --> 00:01:47,640
Give it back!

30
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,310
Wan, are you okay?

31
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:51,970
Lin Xian.

32
00:01:52,420 --> 00:01:53,060
Lin Xian!

33
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:54,830
Lin Xian.

34
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,030
Lin Xian.

35
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:58,360
Didn't you say

36
00:01:58,830 --> 00:02:00,520
you'd explain everything to me?

37
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,780
Please wake up.

38
00:02:04,370 --> 00:02:05,920
Wake up, Lin Xian!

39
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,810
Lin Xian!

40
00:02:25,830 --> 00:02:26,830
Qing Wan,

41
00:02:26,830 --> 00:02:28,270
calm down.

42
00:02:28,270 --> 00:02:29,610
This is just a dream.

43
00:02:30,450 --> 00:02:31,360
He won't die if

44
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,550
you don't want him to.

45
00:02:34,650 --> 00:02:35,950
Wan, what are you talking about?

46
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:40,180
[The Real World]

47
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:53,710
Xian?

48
00:02:54,230 --> 00:02:55,050
Xian!

49
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,540
Xian, what's going on?

50
00:02:56,540 --> 00:02:57,800
Someone, help! Doctor!

51
00:03:07,140 --> 00:03:08,140
His heart rate is abnormal.

52
00:03:08,140 --> 00:03:08,860
Transfer him immediately.

53
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,040
Lin Xian?

54
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:25,380
Lin Xian?

55
00:03:28,610 --> 00:03:29,520
Where am I?

56
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,170
Stay still.

57
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:32,260
The ambulance is coming.

58
00:03:32,830 --> 00:03:33,640
I don't need it.

59
00:03:34,050 --> 00:03:34,890
Take me home.

60
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:38,860
[The Real World]

61
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,520
He wants you.

62
00:03:54,580 --> 00:03:56,550
That depends on whether he'll survive.

63
00:03:56,550 --> 00:03:58,320
What do you mean?

64
00:03:58,320 --> 00:04:00,600
You promised you wouldn't harm him.

65
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:03,800
Do you think you can negotiate?

66
00:04:04,550 --> 00:04:06,420
Got what you wanted
and now you're ditching me?

67
00:04:07,170 --> 00:04:08,210
If you cooperate,

68
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:10,100
I might

69
00:04:10,990 --> 00:04:12,700
leave you a good spot at Stone.

70
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:15,020
If he finds out I was involved,

71
00:04:15,730 --> 00:04:17,390
I'll never be able to stay with him.

72
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,850
Is that really such a big loss?

73
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:21,770
If you do good at Stone,

74
00:04:24,020 --> 00:04:25,760
maybe he'll take more notice of you.

75
00:04:36,740 --> 00:04:38,780
[Unable to exit. Please use the key]

76
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:40,970
He Fan's did this.

77
00:04:52,820 --> 00:04:53,520
Qing Wan,

78
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,790
I need to tell you something.

79
00:04:57,770 --> 00:04:58,640
Go on.

80
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:06,450
It might be hard to digest,

81
00:05:07,910 --> 00:05:09,270
so brace yourself.

82
00:05:24,770 --> 00:05:25,850
When did you find out?

83
00:05:25,850 --> 00:05:27,140
This is my dream, right?

84
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:29,950
When one realizes they're dreaming,

85
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:32,380
they can do whatever they want.

86
00:05:35,450 --> 00:05:36,200
Qing Wan,

87
00:05:37,410 --> 00:05:38,880
have you remembered who you are?

88
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:41,700
I've been wondering

89
00:05:42,740 --> 00:05:44,150
how you would tell me the truth.

90
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,470
"Qing Wan's Forest" is your creation.

91
00:05:47,470 --> 00:05:48,710
It's based on your "Daydream."

92
00:05:49,790 --> 00:05:52,000
You developed Dreamscape
after joining Xian Game.

93
00:05:52,970 --> 00:05:55,000
Right now, you're inside a dream
generated by the engine.

94
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,450
I know all about this already.

95
00:05:59,210 --> 00:06:00,140
About us, do you...?

96
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:00,940
So,

97
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:03,850
what's your agenda?

98
00:06:05,210 --> 00:06:06,000
Agenda?

99
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:08,850
All I've ever wanted was for you

100
00:06:08,850 --> 00:06:09,890
to remember our past

101
00:06:10,150 --> 00:06:11,140
and wake up.

102
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:15,080
You mean the memories
you planted in my mind

103
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,290
to make me fall for you,

104
00:06:16,290 --> 00:06:18,520
just so I'd keep upgrading Dreamscape,
get stuck

105
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:19,700
in my own dream,

106
00:06:19,700 --> 00:06:21,440
and let you steal my work?

107
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:28,910
Qing Wan,

108
00:06:30,770 --> 00:06:31,820
what are you talking about?

109
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:35,740
I don't know either.

110
00:06:36,650 --> 00:06:38,830
And I don't want to believe
you'd actually do this.

111
00:06:39,580 --> 00:06:41,950
But He Fan already told me everything.

112
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:42,890
He Fan?

113
00:06:42,890 --> 00:06:44,080
Him again!

114
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,320
Don't believe him.

115
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,970
He definitely orchestrated
the car accident

116
00:06:46,970 --> 00:06:48,030
and the falling flowerpot!

117
00:06:48,030 --> 00:06:49,560
He wants to trap you!

118
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,880
Then prove you're telling the truth,

119
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,390
that you're not putting on a show!

120
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:58,700
Can't you feel my love for you?

121
00:06:58,700 --> 00:07:00,500
But aren't you supposed
to be all-powerful here?

122
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,650
Qing Wan,

123
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,020
listen to me.

124
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:06,680
Qing Wan!

125
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:08,390
I'm going home.

126
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:09,650
We must stay together.

127
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,150
He won't stop
until he gets what he wants.

128
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,850
We're both in danger now.

129
00:07:18,910 --> 00:07:21,180
That's a neural disruptor
developed by Stone Network.

130
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:22,850
A disruptor?

131
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:26,320
He's been trying to extract memories
from your subconscious.

132
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,210
My memories?

133
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,240
What does he want with them?

134
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:31,320
What he's really after

135
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:33,440
is the core technology
behind Dreamscape.

136
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,210
It's locked in you.

137
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:38,290
But why?

138
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:41,220
Stone has been trying to develop

139
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:43,030
a massively multiplayer online
dream-based game,

140
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,830
but they lack the key engine technology.

141
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:47,080
Now,they're trying to kill us,

142
00:07:48,090 --> 00:07:49,770
it means they already have
what they wanted.

143
00:07:50,530 --> 00:07:51,640
Get rid of us,

144
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,410
and they can do whatever...

145
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:09,520
It's an African bee.

146
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:11,440
Its sting contains a cardiac toxin

147
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:13,620
that acts very quickly.

148
00:08:14,910 --> 00:08:17,320
But these bees are only found
in South Africa and Brazil.

149
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:19,210
They shouldn't be here.

150
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:28,240
The stability of Dreamscape
has also been compromised.

151
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,970
Let me try.

152
00:08:30,970 --> 00:08:32,000
I can probably fix it.

153
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:11,000
Dr. Wu,

154
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,260
[The Real World]
how's Xian doing?

155
00:09:13,310 --> 00:09:16,290
Chairman Lin, I've never encountered
anything like this before.

156
00:09:16,290 --> 00:09:18,880
Dreamscape's ultra-realistic simulation
has tricked his brain,

157
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:21,020
trapping his consciousness inside.

158
00:09:21,780 --> 00:09:23,140
He can't tell dreams from reality.

159
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,480
Right now, the most important thing

160
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,880
is to keep Dreamscape running smoothly

161
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:31,450
and stabilize Miss Qing's condition.

162
00:09:31,450 --> 00:09:34,190
Their minds are now linked.

163
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:35,660
Hurt one, hurt both.

164
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:37,950
I'm counting on you.

165
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:40,660
You must bring Xian back,

166
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:43,240
no matter what it takes!

167
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,020
I'll do my best.

168
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:00,880
Who is it?

169
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:01,790
Go check.

170
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,020
Lin Xian!

171
00:10:10,930 --> 00:10:11,740
Lin Xian?

172
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:12,790
Lin Xian, wake up.

173
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:13,980
Lin Xian?

174
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:15,290
Lin Xian?

175
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:23,240
He Fan?

176
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:39,640
♪The stars in the sky shine bright♪

177
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:43,880
♪The rippling water reflects your face♪

178
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:47,720
♪No one knows the struggle in my mind♪

179
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:51,400
♪I act calm as I say hi♪

180
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:55,320
♪In two different worlds,
we're both rushing ahead♪

181
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:59,240
♪Thinking the view at the top
would leave us breathless♪

182
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:03,200
♪As memories fade like shattered pieces♪

183
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:06,960
♪I still find myself drawn to you♪

184
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:10,760
♪In a crowd of people,
with nowhere to land♪

185
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:14,760
♪Your presence is my island,
my solid ground♪

186
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:17,520
♪I know where you are♪

187
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:19,720
♪But act like I don't care♪

188
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:22,680
♪My heart beats for you,
yet I leave it unsaid♪

189
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:26,940
♪Passion and loneliness
carve our memories♪

190
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:30,860
♪The moonlight by the lighthouse
leaves no trace♪

191
00:11:30,860 --> 00:11:32,660
♪For you, I'd cross mountains and seas♪
